WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.979 --> 00:00:04.200
-Sir, permission to leave the station
-For what purpose Master Chief?

00:00:04.200 --> 00:00:11.200
-To give the Covenant back their bomb.
-Permission granted.

00:00:23.150 --> 00:00:27.199
-I know what you're thinking, and it's crazy.
-So stay here.

00:00:27.199 --> 00:00:34.199
-Unfortunately for us both, I like crazy.

00:00:51.580 --> 00:00:52.580
-Just one question:

00:00:53.740 --> 00:00:55.640
-What if you miss?

00:00:55.680 --> 00:00:56.700
-I won't.

00:02:08.820 --> 00:02:13.540
[Boooooom explosion!]

